text:
31 New MOH? AFSOC to recommend upgrading airman's Air Force Cross 
Military Times: Air Force Special Operations Command plans to recommend that one of the seven airmen who have been awarded the Air Force Cross since Sept. 11 receive the Medal of Honor, said Lt. Gen. Bradley Heithold, AFSOC commander.
